select (CASE
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "KOL" THEN CONCAT("KOL: ", tbl_lead.sub_lead)
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "External Edufair" THEN (CASE WHEN tbl_eduf_lead.title != null THEN CONCAT(tbl_eduf_lead.title) ELSE (CASE WHEN tbl_eduf_lead.sch_id IS NULL THEN ceduf.corp_name ELSE seduf.sch_name END)END)
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "All-In Partners" THEN CONCAT("All-In Partners: ", tbl_corp.corp_name)
ELSE tbl_lead.main_lead
END) AS conversion_lead, COUNT((CASE
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "KOL" THEN CONCAT(tbl_lead.sub_lead)
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "External Edufair" THEN (CASE WHEN tbl_eduf_lead.title != null THEN CONCAT(tbl_eduf_lead.title) ELSE (CASE WHEN tbl_eduf_lead.sch_id IS NULL THEN ceduf.corp_name ELSE seduf.sch_name END)END)
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "All-In Partners" THEN CONCAT(tbl_corp.corp_name)
ELSE tbl_lead.main_lead
END)) AS count_conversionLead from `tbl_client_event` left join `tbl_lead` on `tbl_lead`.`lead_id` = `tbl_client_event`.`lead_id` left join `tbl_eduf_lead` on `tbl_eduf_lead`.`id` = `tbl_client_event`.`eduf_id` left join `tbl_corp` on `tbl_corp`.`corp_id` = `tbl_client_event`.`partner_id` left join `tbl_corp` as `ceduf` on `ceduf`.`corp_id` = `tbl_eduf_lead`.`corp_id` left join `tbl_sch` as `seduf` on `seduf`.`sch_id` = `tbl_eduf_lead`.`sch_id` where month(`tbl_client_event`.`created_at`) = '11' and year(`tbl_client_event`.`created_at`) = '2023' group by `conversion_lead`
